      "span_text": "However, the number of common lymphoid progenitor (CLP) cells was significantly reduced in Cgt ÿ/ÿ mice compared to Cgt +/+ littermates ( Figure 1C ), indicating that the previously reported block in lymphoid differentiation occurs before the CLP stage."
